node.text: ✨Answering questions and New Aura Reveal!!✨Hi Everyone!! Thank you all so much for the love and support on my recent designs!!! I am so grateful for all your wonderful comments and dms! My next restock will be on August 13th at 7pm eastern time. I ship worldwide. My prices range from $45 to $250. The link to my website is in my bio. All crystals used in my decor are real. The new crystal auras I have been posting are my brand auras, I don’t buy them from anyone and yes I’ll have some for sale next restock.🥰And a sneak peak of a new Aura Crystal that has yet to be named!!! I know I already posted Ember, which is a hot pink red. Well this beauty embodies fire and it kinda reminds me of the philosophers stone from Harry Potter!😍Help me name this new aura crystal and comment below!! If I choose your suggested name I’ll send you free crystal goodies🥰🥰

node.text: Is it true Instagram will no longer be a photo sharing app??!!😵I’ve noticed a massive drop in views on my photos recently and after posting about it this week the top comment was instagrams newest update. So I did some research and found that although the app will still allow photos to be shared, it’s main goal is to be more like TikTok. Focusing more on promoting reels and videos. I honestly wish Instagram would stop changing everything about this app and give us back the chronological feed💔Thank you all again for commenting on my recent post and dm’ing me about this issue. Have a blessed day everyone !!!🌸✨
